data.meta_description: The track width is the distance between the wheel centres along the transverse axis of the vehicle. The track width is 1250 mm on the front axle and 930 mm on the rear axle.
data.text: The track width is the distance between the wheel centres along the transverse axis of the vehicle. The track width is 1255 mm on the front axle and 935 mm on the rear axle.
